title: Verify the blank response through provisioner API
custom_steps:
1. Use the provisoner API to place a certain category.
curl -v -H 'Content-Type: application/json' -d '{"advance-silent-block-options":{"blank-response":["80","70"],"suppress-events":["99"]}}' http://provisionervip:6400/dp/config/sync?tenantid=1225
custom_expected: NOTE: In this case, since Online-Ad cateogy is not aded in blank-response and suppress-event, default behavior of Online-Ad category will not apply.
